"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?13/59/14264/abstract/2\">",
"      Jacobson SH, Ekl&ouml;f O, Eriksson CG, et al. Development of hypertension and uraemia after pyelonephritis in childhood: 27 year follow up. BMJ 1989; 299:703.",
"     </a>",
